{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.setItem()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><em><code>setItem()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Storage API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a> インターフェイスの <code>setItem()</code> メソッドはキーの名称と値を渡すと、ストレージにキーを追加する、またはキーがすでに存在する場合はキーに対する値を更新します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>storage</em>.setItem(<em>keyName</em>, <em>keyValue</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"keyname\"><em>keyName</em></dt>\n <dd>作成または更新したいキーの名称を持つ <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"keyvalue\"><em>keyValue</em></dt>\n <dd>作成または更新するキーに対して渡したい値を持つ <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>戻り値なし。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns_2","title":"例外","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>setItem()</code> は、ストレージが満杯である場合に例外が発生します。特に Mobile Safari (iOS 5 以降) では、ユーザがプライベートモードに入っているときに必ず例外が発生します (Safari はプライベートモードで、クォータを 0 バイトに設定します。一方他のブラウザは別のデータコンテナを使用して、プライベートモードでもストレージを使用できます)。<br>\n 従って開発者は、<strong><code>setItem()</code> で発生する可能性がある例外を常にキャッチする</strong>ようにしてください。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の関数はローカルストレージに 3 個のデータアイテムを作成します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'myCat.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>注記</strong>: 実際の例として、<a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/web-storage/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a> をご覧ください。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-storage-setitem\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"ja\">setItem() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">不明</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Storage.setItem","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\">Storage.getItem()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\">Storage.removeItem()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API を使用する</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Storage インターフェイスの setItem() メソッドはキーの名称と値を渡すと、ストレージにキーを追加する、またはキーがすでに存在する場合はキーに対する値を更新します。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/storage/setitem","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/storage/setitem/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage","title":"Storage"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem","title":"Storage.setItem()"}],"pageTitle":"Storage.setItem() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}